data.title: Census: Population: Uttar Pradesh: Kairana
data.meta_description: Census: Population: Uttar Pradesh: Kairana data was reported at 89,000.000 Person in Mar 2011. This records an increase from the previous number of 73,011.000 Person for Mar 2001. Census: Population: Uttar Pradesh: Kairana data is updated decadal, averaging 24,808.500 Person (Median) from Mar 1901 to 03-01-2011, with 12 observations. The data reached an all-time high of 89,000.000 Person in 03-01-2011 and a record low of 16,293.000 Person in 03-01-1911. Census: Population: Uttar Pradesh: Kairana data remains active status in CEIC and is reported by Office of the Registrar General & Census Commissioner, India. The data is categorized under India Premium Database’s Demographic – Table IN.GAC035: Census: Population: By Towns and Urban Agglomerations: Uttar Pradesh.
